name: HIKARI 光
description:
LEOM KOLMNELA
There is a light that shines at the bottom of the horizons,
I would like to catch up with her and see who she can be.
I don't know how long the journey takes, passing plains and mountains,
but I want to get to where it looks best.

That light has a face, like one I knew,
that shone like this and that illuminated the same.
If it were like that, I don't know what would happen to me,
but I would go for her to the end.
